### Base URL (⚠️ replace with your Codespaces URL)
@baseUrl = https://super-duper-adventure-54vv779q69gc4wj-5088.app.github.dev
@token = my-secret-token

### -----------------------------------
### ✅ GET all users (SUCCESS)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### ❌ GET all users (NO TOKEN - should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users

###

### ❌ GET all users (INVALID TOKEN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: wrong-token

###

### ✅ CREATE new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "role": "Admin"
}

###

### ✅ GET user by ID (after POST)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### ✅ UPDATE user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "name": "John Updated",
  "email": "john@updated.com",
  "role": "User"
}

###

### ✅ DELETE user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### ❌ DELETE non-existing user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/999
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### ❌ CREATE invalid user (validation test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "invalid",
  "role": ""
}

###
